These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
There 2 different types of food: grapes, cabbage
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, november
1. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food           | cabbage | grapes |
| Birthday   | november     | september  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, tennis
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Sport         | tennis   | climbing      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
House: modern, townhouse
2 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| House   | townhouse | modern    |
| Game     | monopoly | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
City: marseilles, liverpool
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea
1. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| City   | marseilles   | liverpool |
| Flower   | lily | azalea |

 #################################

 
